## Quick Start

### Prerequisites
- Docker 20.10+
- Docker Compose 2.20+
- 4GB RAM minimum

### Installation

1. **Clone and setup:**
```bash
git clone <repository-url>
cd fastfood-docker


sudo docker run -d \
  --name fastfood-db \
  -e POSTGRES_USER=fastfood_admin \
  -e POSTGRES_PASSWORD=SecurePass123! \
  -e POSTGRES_DB=fastfood_db \
  -p 5432:5432 \
  -v $(pwd)/init.sql:/tmp/init.sql \
  fastfood-app-db:latest




 git add . && git commit -m "Your commit message" && git push origin main
